[assistant] 
[assistant] What it covers:
[assistant] - Generates a real LMS private key through the Bouncy Castle PQC JCA provider.
[assistant] - Serializes it with `ObjectOutputStream.writeObject(...)`, reaching `BCLMSPrivateKey.writeObject`.
[assistant] - Deserializes it with `ObjectInputStream.readObject()`, reaching `BCLMSPrivateKey.readObject`.
[assistant] - Verifies the restored key preserves algorithm, format, LMS levels, usage state, encoding, equality, and hash code.
[assistant] - Includes repeated serialization of the restored key to keep the path exercised beyond the initial instance.
