ify the test to use replacing streams, which might include adding assertions. The current test passes with normal cases, but I notice it doesn’t cover everything. I should definitely add a test with serialization substitution hooks or switch to replacement streams for serialization/de-serialization helpers.\"}]}"}, {"type": "toolCall", "id": "call_ms59iE22lhma1ZuS8JZ4tGPS|fc_0dcdbe9992fcc2a6016a2633d0ca388190b86fc4734f1f40b6", "name": "bash", "arguments": {"command": "grep -R \"static class\\|static final class\\|implements Serializable\" -n tests/src/org.bouncycastle/bcprov-jdk15to18/1.77/src/test/java/org_bouncycastle/bcprov_jdk15to18 | head -50"}}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "oca/gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 1038, "output": 2074, "cacheRead": 41472, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 44584, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "toolUse", "timestamp": 1780888485653, "responseId": "resp_0dcdbe9992fcc2a6016a2633a671608190b5817d2f17878d7b"}, "toolResults": [{"role": "toolResult", "toolCallId": "call_ms59iE22lhma1ZuS8JZ4tGPS|fc_0dcdbe9992fcc2a6016a2633d0ca388190b86fc4734f1f40b6", "toolName": "bash", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "tests/src/org.bouncycastle/bcprov-jdk15to18/1.77/src/test/java/org_bouncycastle/bcprov_jdk15to18/BCKyberPublicKeyTest.java:120:    private static final class PublicKeyHolder implements Serializable {\ntests/src/org.bouncycastle/bcprov-jdk15to18/1.77/src/test/java/org_bouncycastle/bcprov_jdk15to18/BCGOST3410PrivateKeyTest.java:96:    private static final class BCGOST3410PrivateKeyObjectOutputStream\ntests/src/org.bouncycastle/bcprov-jdk15to18/1.77/src/test/java/org_bouncycastle/bcprov_jdk15to18/BCGOST3410PrivateKeyTest.java:139:    private static final class BCGOST3410PrivateKeyObjectInputStream\ntests/src/org.bouncycastle/bcprov-jdk15to18/1.77/src/test/java/org_bouncycastle/bcprov_jdk15to18/JournaledAlgorithmTest.java:65:    private static final class F